│ Condition is often uniform\n        }\n        \n        // For other       │
│ cases, use the standard method but with a fallback\n        // that assumes │
│ first lane usage if the standard method fails\n        bool StandardResult  │
│ = U.onlyFirstLaneUsed(RepR);\n        \n        // If the standard result   │
│ is false, but this is a simple operation\n        // on what should be a    │
